fg_segments: /** * Override styles for elements with color depending on brand, product type, etc. */

/* TODO: This should be written in BEM to avoid accumulation of specificity */ .accent-color__font-color, .product__cta--accent-color a, .rail-buttons__link-anchor--accent-color, .rail-buttons__link-anchor--accent-color:hover, .product__benefit-item--accent-color:before, .end-uses__item--accent-color:before, .product-specs__heading--accent-color, .brand

-body-copy__header--accent-color, .brand__range-header--accent-color, .brand__finishes-header--accent-color, .finishes-carousel__finish-name--accent-color, .finishes-carousel__looks-header--accent-color, .finishes-carousel__feels-header--accent-color, .title--brand{ color: #2a68b5; }
/* TODO: The data circle is not in BEM.
But I don't know how to do double, dependent modifiers... yet.

*/ .accent-color__background-color, .product__cta--accent-color, .product__ribbon--accent-color, .rail-buttons--accent-color, .rail--horizontal.rail--accent-color, .node-type-product .field-name-field-product-end-uses li::before, .node-type-product .field-name-field-sustain-info-li li::before, .sg-product-dots__dot--shaded{ background-color: #2a68b5; }
/* TODO: This should be written in BEM to avoid accumulation of specificity */ .product__cta--accent-color a:before, .rail-buttons__link--accent-color:before { border-right-color: #2a68b5; }

/* TODO: This should be written in BEM to avoid accumulation of specificity */ .product__cta--accent-color a:after, .rail-buttons__link--accent-color:after { border-right-color: #2a68b5; border-top-color: #2a68b5; }

.relevant-links__download-icon--accent-color, .product__datasheet-icon--accent-color, .testimonial__icon-open--accent-color, .testimonial__icon-close--accent-color, .product-specs__datasheet-icon--accent-color, .product-features-table__file-icon--accent-color{ fill: #2a68b5; }

/* TODO: NOT mobile-first */ @media only screen and (max-width: 480px){ .accent-color__background-color--screen-small, .product__benefits-label--accent-color, .end-uses__label--accent-color, .product-features__header--accent-color{ background-color: #2a68b5; } }
/* TODO: NOT mobile-first */ @media only screen and (max-width: 768px){ /* TODO: The collapsed header is not in BEM.
But I don't know how to do double, dependent modifiers... yet.
*/ .accordion-page-section__header--accent-color.accordion-page-section__header--collapsed{ background-color: #2a68b5; } }
